[package]
name = "bank"
build = "build.rs"

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[package.metadata.cargo-shear]
ignored = ["prost"]

[dependencies]
prost = "0.14.1"
reqwest = "0.12.28"

[build-dependencies]
prost-build = "0.14.1"

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "bank"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "process"

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[dependencies]
chrono = "0.4.42"
indicatif = "0.18.3"
regex = "1.12.2"
serde_json = "1.0.145"

[dependencies.bank]
path = "../bank"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.53"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.24"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.228"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.48.0"
features = ["full"]

[features]
verbose = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "process"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "process"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "server"

[package.edition]
workspace = true

[package.version]
workspace = true

[dependencies]
meilisearch-sdk = "0.31.0"
once_cell = "1.21.3"
tracing = "0.1.43"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.8.7"
features = ["macros"]

[dependencies.bank]
path = "../bank"

[dependencies.redis]
version = "1.0"
features = ["tokio-comp", "connection-manager"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.228"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.48.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.6.7"
features = ["cors"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter"]

[features]
verbose = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "server"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "server"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]
